section.note:
@note If you need to resume subscribing to the video streams of remote users in the channel after calling \ref IRtcEngine::setDefaultMuteAllRemoteVideoStreams "setDefaultMuteAllRemoteVideoStreams" (true), do the following:
If you need to resume subscribing to a single user's video stream, call () and specify the ID of the remote user you want to subscribe to.
If you want to resume subscribing to video streams of multiple users, you need to call () multiple times.
